{"title_page": "Anna R\u0119dzia", "text_new": "{{Infobox football biography\n| name           = Anna R\u0119dzia\n| image          = \n| image_size     = \n| caption        =\n| fullname       = \n| birth_date     = {{Birth date and age|df=yes|1996|10|2}}<ref name=SW>{{Soccerway|id=185453|accessdate=16 April 2020}}</ref>\n| birth_place    = \n| height         = \n| position       = [[Midfielder]]<ref>{{UEFA player|id=250027430|accessdate=16 April 2020}}</ref>\n| currentclub    = [[UKS SMS \u0141\u00f3d\u017a<!-- women -->]]\n| clubnumber     = 10\n| youthyears1    = \n| youthclubs1    = \n| collegeyears1  = \n| college1       = \n| collegecaps1   = | collegegoals1 = \n| years1         = \n| clubs1         = [[UKS SMS \u0141\u00f3d\u017a<!-- women -->]]\n| caps1          = \n| goals1         = \n| nationalyears1 = 2011\u20132013\n| nationalteam1  = {{Nwftu|17|Poland}}\n| nationalcaps1  = 17\n| nationalgoals1 = 0\n| nationalyears2 = 2013\u20132014\n| nationalteam2  = {{Nwftu|19|Poland}}\n| nationalcaps2  = 8\n| nationalgoals2 = 0\n| nationalyears3 = 2014\u2013\n| nationalteam3  = [[Poland women's national football team|Poland]]\n| nationalcaps3  = 5\n| nationalgoals3 = 0\n| pcupdate = \n| ntupdate = 12 November 2019\n}}\n'''Anna R\u0119dzia''' (born 2 October 1996) is a Polish [[women's association football|footballer]] who plays as a [[midfielder]] for [[Ekstraliga (women's football)|Ekstraliga]] club [[UKS SMS \u0141\u00f3d\u017a<!-- women -->]] and the [[Poland women's national football team|Poland women's national team]].\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n*{{Cite web|url=https://ukssmslodz.pl/player/anna-r%c4%99dzia/|title=Anna R\u0119dzia|website=UKS SMS \u0141\u00f3d\u017a|language=pl|accessdate=16 April 2020}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:R\u0119dzia, Anna}}\n[[Category:1996 births]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:Women's association football midfielders]]\n[[Category:Polish women's footballers]]\n[[Category:Poland women's international footballers]]\n[[Category:UKS SMS \u0141\u00f3d\u017a<!-- women --> players]]\n\n\n{{Poland-women-footy-bio-stub}}\n", "text_old": "{{Infobox football biography\n| name           = Anna R\u0119dzia\n| image          = \n| image_size     = \n| caption        =\n| fullname       = \n| birth_date     = {{Birth date and age|df=yes|1996|10|2}}<ref name=SW>{{Soccerway|id=185453|accessdate=16 April 2020}}</ref>\n| birth_place    = \n| height         = \n| position       = [[Midfielder]]<ref>{{UEFA player|id=250027430|accessdate=16 April 2020}}</ref>\n| currentclub    = [[UKS SMS \u0141\u00f3d\u017a<!-- women -->]]\n| clubnumber     = 10\n| youthyears1    = \n| youthclubs1    = \n| collegeyears1  = \n| college1       = \n| collegecaps1   = | collegegoals1 = \n| years1         = \n| clubs1         = [[UKS SMS \u0141\u00f3d\u017a<!-- women -->]]\n| caps1          = \n| goals1         = \n| nationalyears1 = 2011\u20132013\n| nationalteam1  = {{Nwftu|17|Poland}}\n| nationalcaps1  = 17\n| nationalgoals1 = 0\n| nationalyears2 = 2013\u20132014\n| nationalteam2  = {{Nwftu|19|Poland}}\n| nationalcaps2  = 8\n| nationalgoals2 = 0\n| nationalyears3 = 2014\u2013\n| nationalteam3  = [[Poland women's national football team|Poland]]\n| nationalcaps3  = 5\n| nationalgoals3 = 0\n| pcupdate = \n| ntupdate = 12 November 2019\n}}\n'''Anna R\u0119dzia''' (born 2 October 1996) is a Polish [[women's association football|footballer]] who plays as a [[midfielder]] for [[Ekstraliga (women's football)|Ekstraliga]] club [[UKS SMS \u0141\u00f3d\u017a<!-- women -->]] and the [[Poland women's national football team|Poland women's national team]].\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n*{{Cite web|url=https://ukssmslodz.pl/player/anna-r%c4%99dzia/|title=Anna R\u0119dzia|website=UKS SMS \u0141\u00f3d\u017a|language=pl|accessdate=16 April 2020}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:R\u0119dzia, Anna}}\n[[Category:1996 births]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:Women's association football midfielders]]\n[[Categor